to the Sensei.

420
00:37:18,570 --> 00:37:20,600
What do you think of this?

421
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:31,210
A paid companion.

422
00:37:32,150 --> 00:37:33,550
Perfect.

423
00:37:34,250 --> 00:37:36,390
Wouldn't that
intimidate Tanigawa?

424
00:37:36,390 --> 00:37:39,340
Sakuragi Erika-chan, age 17.
A senior at Teito High School.

425
00:37:39,340 --> 00:37:40,990
Is she a high school student?

426
00:37:40,990 --> 00:37:44,130
She's been doing it for
a while through a circle.

427
00:37:44,130 --> 00:37:46,600
Her father is a Section
Chief of a major bank,

428
00:37:46,600 --> 00:37:48,600
and her mother is a
full-time housewife.

429
00:37:48,600 --> 00:37:51,100
