to back down.

430
00:37:52,670 --> 00:37:55,820
Can I get paid for it?

431
00:37:55,820 --> 00:37:57,000
Stop it.

432
00:38:00,310 --> 00:38:02,140
So this is your job...

433
00:38:03,780 --> 00:38:05,680
This is what you
do for a living.

434
00:38:06,950 --> 00:38:08,560
What're you getting at?

435
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:10,890
You investigate on the
person's private lifestyle

436
00:38:10,890 --> 00:38:12,760
and you make
a living off of that.

437
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:15,020
Is that what you were
going to treat me with?

438
00:38:18,430 --> 00:38:20,880
I'm sorry. She's still a kid.

439
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:23,303
Why didn't you stop the
crime before it happened?

440
00:38:23,303 --> 00:38:24,850
What?

441
00:38:24,850 --> 00:38:27,110
