she could've been killed.

443
00:38:29,820 --> 00:38:31,820
So why didn't you stop
them before they went in?

444
00:38:31,820 --> 00:38:34,350
Is she your friend?

445
00:38:34,350 --> 00:38:36,310
She has nothing
to do with us.

446
00:38:37,450 --> 00:38:39,190
Nothing to do with you?

447
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:42,060
That's right. I just
did my job.

448
00:38:42,060 --> 00:38:44,060
It doesn't matter to me
what happens to the person.

449
00:38:44,060 --> 00:38:46,060
Oh yes, it does! You
were there watching it!

450
00:38:46,060 --> 00:38:49,000
What have I done that
deserves your criticism?

451
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:51,600
- Am I wrong?
- You're not wrong at all.

452
00:38:51,600 --> 00:38:55,050
It's your friend and that
man that are wrong.

453
00:38:55,050 --> 00:38:57,290
If you have time to take
photos, then stop them.

454
00:38:57,290 --> 00:38:58,730
Why should I?

455
00:38:59,470 --> 00:39:02,770
A woman who wants money.
A man who buys her with money.

456
00:39:02,770 --> 00:39:04,450
They're both doing it
at their free will.

457
