They're in agreement
with each other.

458
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:09,740
It's not my business
if Tanigawa kills Erika.

459
00:39:11,550 --> 00:39:14,320
You're the worst.

460
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,920
You know...

461
00:39:23,990 --> 00:39:25,930
What do you think
you're doing!?

462
00:39:33,240 --> 00:39:35,400
