465
00:39:47,780 --> 00:39:49,350
Screw you!

466
00:40:10,530 --> 00:40:12,100
Hey!

467
00:40:25,410 --> 00:40:27,380
Don't have
expectations of me.

468
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:34,750
I'm not like that.

469
00:40:59,610 --> 00:41:02,180
There's always "that"
possibility for a girl.

470
00:41:10,550 --> 00:41:14,830
A child like me, who didn't
know of her papa, can be born.

471
00:41:30,270 --> 00:41:32,410
You're a scum to society.

472
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:08,070
This guarantees our
victory in the lawsuit.

473
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:12,600
This is the pay for this
job. Give it to Shinpei.

474
00:42:16,240 --> 00:42:18,110
Don't show such a sad smile.

475
00:42:22,420 --> 00:42:24,780
Shinpei! We got paid!

476
00:42:25,420 --> 00:42:27,450
She's so immature.

477
00:42:28,320 --> 00:42:30,620
Deliver the negatives
and photos later.

478
00:42:31,720 --> 00:42:33,110
You know...

479
00:42:33,110 --> 00:42:34,690
I'm not increasing the pay.

480
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,860
I'm dropping out of this one.

481
00:42:40,700 --> 00:42:43,540
What are you saying?
Are you stupid?

482
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:47,040
Don't be fettered by her.

483
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:50,080
This is a lucrative job.

484
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:53,750
You get paid this much
for two days of work.

485
00:42:53,750 --> 00:42:55,600
400,000 yen for two days!

486
00:42:55,600 --> 00:42:56,980
Isn't that a great job?

487
00:42:59,150 --> 00:43:01,290
I don't like the way
