488
00:43:23,300 --> 00:43:25,370
<i>She's very naive.</i>

489
00:43:26,670 --> 00:43:30,180
<i>She's exactly like Yukino-chan.</i>

490
00:43:31,040 --> 00:43:32,580
<i>Yukino?</i>

491
00:43:33,750 --> 00:43:35,580
<i>Marimo's mother.</i>

492
00:43:36,780 --> 00:43:40,340
<i>She was a caring and
righteous person.</i>

493
00:43:40,344 --> 00:43:41,750
<i>Did you know her?</i>

494
00:43:42,960 --> 00:43:47,160
<i>I defended him eight times
as a public prosecutor and</i>

495
00:43:47,160 --> 00:43:49,700
six times after
I went on my own.

496
00:43:50,660 --> 00:43:52,770
He's the worst.

497
00:43:52,776 --> 00:43:55,470
They were all for self-defense.

498
00:43:58,370 --> 00:44:02,270
He's running hard for
the sake of others.

499
00:44:06,280 --> 00:44:09,350
In the last case
I defended him in...

