was picked on in town.

501
00:44:15,320 --> 00:44:17,730
The guy was a total stranger.

502
00:44:17,736 --> 00:44:19,590
It's not normal, right?

503
00:44:22,190 --> 00:44:25,830
That night, at the hospital
he was rushed to,

504
00:44:25,830 --> 00:44:28,730
he met with Yukino-chan.

505
00:44:40,610 --> 00:44:44,680
He's not legally bound to
take care of Marimo, but

506
00:44:44,680 --> 00:44:48,650
Yukino-chan entrusted Marimo
in Shinpei's care.

507
00:44:49,890 --> 00:44:53,130
Her dearly beloved daughter.

508
00:44:54,030 --> 00:44:56,500
So they aren't real
father and daughter?

509
00:45:02,700 --> 00:45:10,300
I wonder if he'll change...

510
00:45:10,300 --> 00:45:13,700
...after meeting Marimo.

511
00:47:46,780 --> 00:47:48,350
What's wrong?

512
00:47:48,720 --> 00:47:51,520
Satoi-san gave me this.

513
00:47:57,690 --> 00:47:59,990
These are the
negatives and photos.

514
00:48:05,430 --> 00:48:07,970
Please be sure to win
against that Tanigawa guy.

515
00:48:08,900 --> 00:48:10,200
See you later.

516
00:48:15,610 --> 00:48:17,340
What are you doing?

517
00:48:25,420 --> 00:48:27,390
You don't get paid for it.

518
00:48:28,390 --> 00:48:30,660
You didn't do any work.

519
00:48:34,200 --> 00:48:37,270
It was premature work.

520
00:48:37,270 --> 00:48:39,600
So I won't pay you for it.

521
00:48:45,000 --> 00:48:46,600
Shinpei.

522
00:48:54,550 --> 00:48:58,150
What were those tears
for anyway?

523
00:49:01,360 --> 00:49:03,560
