524
00:49:33,400 --> 00:49:38,400
<i>Mama... why did you
leave me alone?</i>

525
00:49:55,530 --> 00:49:57,260
I searched all over for you!

526
00:50:00,330 --> 00:50:01,770
What is it?

527
00:50:06,370 --> 00:50:08,610
I lost my pay because of you.

528
00:51:20,480 --> 00:51:22,320
I'll be straight with you!

529
00:51:23,850 --> 00:51:25,990
I'm not registering you
as my daughter!

530
00:51:25,990 --> 00:51:27,290
